creator: Food & Safety ltd
descriptionHtml:
Looking to satisfy your craving or forgot to pick up the food on your way home? Food & Safety project No. 1 Pizza & Kebab Shop is here to satisfy your hunger.

Variety of Restaurants Branches Added for You, Brows Menu so you can order Dish of Your Choice Like Pizza Burgers Fast Food Grill to Indian Curry. We’ve got it all – fast delivery, unlimited options, easy online payment and vouchers all at your fingertips.

Live Order Tracking: No more calling the restaurant to check if your order is prepared or picked. On Food & Safety, you’ll be able to live track your delivery right from the restaurant to your doorstep.

How It Works

• Browse to see restaurants and their menu
• Place Order
• Pay via debit/credit card/Wallet
• Track your order in real-time
• Enjoy your meal
• Repeat!

We are adding New Restaurants Branches on Daily Basis so You Can Order Food of Your Choice with variety.
